    <item>
      <title>南非非国大多数席位消失，别无选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-africa-election-anc-has-no-good-options-as-majority-vanishes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨自信地预测执政党将轻松保持其三十年来的政治控制权几个小时后，越来越明显的是，选民有其他想法——这将使这个国家陷入未知的领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-africa-election-anc-has-no-good-options-as-majority-vanishes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克就加密货币问题为特朗普提供建议，彰显亿万富翁的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/musk-counsels-trump-on-crypto-in-sign-of-billionaire-s-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，埃隆·马斯克和唐纳德·特朗普正在讨论加密货币政策，前总统在竞选过程中越来越多地强调比特币和其他数字资产是吸引新选民的一种方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/musk-counsels-trump-on-crypto-in-sign-of-billionaire-s-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:32:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普陪审团重新审理小报如何掩盖模特故事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-re-hears-account-of-how-tabloid-buried-model-s-story</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将决定唐纳德·特朗普命运的纽约陪审团于周四开始了第二天的审议，再次听取了有关《国家询问报》出版商如何“撤下”关于特朗普的负面报道的证词。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-re-hears-account-of-how-tabloid-buried-model-s-story</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默的副手表示资深议员阿博特应该参加选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/rayner-says-abbott-should-be-allowed-to-stand-again-for-labour</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党副领袖安吉拉·雷纳 (Angela Rayner) 表示，资深国会议员黛安·阿博特 (Diane Abbott) 应该被允许参加 7 月 4 日的大选，这表明工党高层在对待这位左翼议员的方式上存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/rayner-says-abbott-should-be-allowed-to-stand-again-for-labour</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:28:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克工资上涨或导致 IMF 付款延迟至 2025 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/mozambique-s-surging-wage-bill-may-delay-imf-payment-to-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份文件显示，由于莫桑比克公共工资支出不断膨胀，该国从国际货币基金组织获得的下一笔付款面临被推迟的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/mozambique-s-surging-wage-bill-may-delay-imf-payment-to-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:25:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
